reviewText: The Simpson's always good for a laugh, even though the best seasons were the first 10 or so.  I can still get a good laught from this American Family.

I'm the kind of guy that wants the booklets and cases and even the covers to be included.  And I mean those extra covers that really serve no purpose, you know what I mean?  It's like a housing for the rest of the actual case?  Anyway, this was missing that .02c plastic sleeve and that irritated me to no end.  Other than that, it's a used item and showed some wear and tear as advertised.

Classic Simpson episodes. Only reason I gave it four stars is because they charge $20 more so they can glue a mold on the original box of Otto' s head. I wish they would go back to the ones like homer was. They where worth the extra money.

If you are a Simpsons fan. You have to own this one too.  I loved it and was happy with the package and when it came.  I would also like to mention that it was a good price considering its a collector and just released as of this year.  Get yourselves a copy and don't wait to start laughing over and over again.
I love the dimension of the box head and the otto had is a great classic character.  Includes evita and grinch and catch me if you can parody
You got to love the Simpsons.  You can not go wrong with this tape.  Love the Molded head's boxes.  Great product.
LOVE THIS SEASON!  Actually, love them all.  This has some of my favorite shows--Homer and Marge drinking together and Homer as Death.
the simpsons have delivered once again  with the hilarious 15th season. the only draw back i have is they take to long to release the seasons. HELLO we will buy them all lets get moving

As with all the Simpsons Limited Collector's editions, Season 15 is awesome with Otto's pop out head on the cover. It is covered with a hard plastic to protect the cover, and the discs inside are snug in the pop out DVD cases. There are extras such as deleted scenes and Matt Groening's greeting. This is a must for all Simpsons fans!!!

My son loved this . He's collecting them all .
Thank you !
Great show.  Delivered quickly and in great condition.  Thank you.
Item arived promptly and as described.
It's the Simpsons! Some episodes are better than others but you can't go wrong unless you're not a fan period. I get the mold head cases for my son and this one arrived well packed safe & sound.
It was a gift that was very happily received!
A permanent archive of this epic show's 16th season, in a delightful collectors' package.  No serious fan of the Simpsons should be without it.

another great simpons collection, well packaged
all the episodes were great, laughed from start till the end
the tree house of horrors was great as always

Thanks

We had it already, so returned it.  Its still a good collection.  Go Otto Man - just don't drive my bus!
